text: Etzelkofen was a municipality in the administrative district of Bern- Mittelland in the canton of Bern, Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipalities of Etzelkofen, Büren zum Hof, Grafenried, Limpach, Mülchi, Schalunen and Zauggenried merged into the municipality of Fraubrunnen.
